{"tid":1873623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 長康邨康美樓室內環境 去水U型喉係廁所入面","createTime":"2020-02-10T18:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T18:40:14.000Z","uid":73407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad0e1545cc0e8d2af39821da79b494fedfccddf6","tid":1873623,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"長康邨康美樓係Y2型公屋 1986年落成<br />\n因為搵唔到康美樓資料<br />\n所以參考同樣係Y2型 1984年落成既青衣邨宜居樓同宜業樓<br />\n平面圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unD5cCB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunD5cCB.jpg&h=134891ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gW1qXbV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgW1qXbV.png&h=4ef5ca81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廁所係正中間<br />\n<br />\n室內片段: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vM-oSJeBedY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvM-oSJeBedY&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4RV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=496f0ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vM-oSJeBedY</a><br />\n廁所由1:22秒開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8lOjufmUmxs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8lOjufmUmxs&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4RV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=55047149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8lOjufmUmxs</a><br />\n廁所由43秒開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sdaIVkCgcWo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsdaIVkCgcWo&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4RV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=788b62ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sdaIVkCgcWo</a><br />\n廁所56秒開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD喉好亂 未睇得明邊條係佢所講既排氣喉<br />\n但所有去水喉都係廁所入面<br />\n只要其中一條有滲漏都有機會傳播病毒<br />\n<br />\n同樣係Y2型既大廈:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Y%E5%9E%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88\" data-sr-url=\"h